HEADWORD: Serous
<hw>Se"rous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>s⟦eacute⟧reux</ets>. See <er>Serum</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Thin; watery; like serum;
